{"id":1683,"date":"2017-07-13T09:10:55","date_gmt":"2017-07-13T09:10:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=1683"},"modified":"2020-12-14T15:04:16","modified_gmt":"2020-12-14T15:04:16","slug":"setup-realtime-notifications-with-pusher-com","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/setup-realtime-notifications-with-pusher-com\/","title":{"rendered":"Setup Realtime Notifications with Pusher.com"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This option is for real-time notifications, which means that you won&#8217;t need to refresh the page in case there is a notification.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Before, when new notifications for a user was added you needed to refresh the page in order the notifications to be updated. Now in this case the notification will be real time and will be shown immediately in Perfex CRM on the top right side.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>First you need to register to Pusher.com website to use their services. Click <a href=\"https:\/\/pusher.com\/signup\">here <\/a>to register if you haven&#8217;t registered already.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Login to pusher.com<\/strong> with your account and on the channels section, click <strong>Manage <\/strong>as shown on the screenshot below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"358\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-manage-channels-1024x358.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4234\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-manage-channels-1024x358.png 1024w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-manage-channels-300x105.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-manage-channels-768x268.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-manage-channels-60x21.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-manage-channels-150x52.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-manage-channels.png 1265w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At the top right side, click <strong>Create App<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A popup window will be shown to create your new application.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>Name your app<\/strong> &#8211; for example: <strong>Perfex CRM<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Select a cluster<\/strong> &#8211; By default pusher.com will select your cluster, you can change it if its needed. You can read more here what is cluster:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/pusher.com\/docs\/clusters\">https:\/\/pusher.com\/docs\/clusters<\/a><\/li><li><strong>Frond-end tech stack<\/strong> &#8211; Select <strong>jQuery <\/strong>as shown in the image below.<\/li><li><strong>Back-end tech stasck?<\/strong> &#8211; Select <strong>PHP<\/strong> as shown in the image below<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"620\" height=\"670\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-create-app.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4235\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-create-app.png 620w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-create-app-278x300.png 278w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-create-app-56x60.png 56w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-create-app-139x150.png 139w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on <strong>Create app<\/strong> at the bottom of the popup modal.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After the app is created click on the <strong>App Keys <\/strong>sidebar menu and on the right side you will be able to see you app keys that needs to be added in <strong>Setup->Settings->Pusher.com<\/strong> in <strong>your Perfex CRM admin are<\/strong>a. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"876\" height=\"561\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-app-keys.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4236\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-app-keys.jpg 876w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-app-keys-300x192.jpg 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-app-keys-768x492.jpg 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-app-keys-60x38.jpg 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/pusher-app-keys-150x96.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 876px) 100vw, 876px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Add the keys to the corresponding fields.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>app_id <\/strong>= APP ID field<\/li><li><strong>key <\/strong>= APP Key field<\/li><li><strong>secret <\/strong>= APP Secret field<\/li><li><strong>cluster<\/strong> = Cluster field<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>After you add the keys set <strong>Enable Real Time Notifications<\/strong> to <strong>Yes <\/strong>and save setting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>That will be all when setting up Pusher.com realtime notifications with Perfex CRM.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Desktop Notifications<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are using version 1.9.0 or above you can configure desktop notifications together with Pusher, keep in mind that desktop notifications require pusher configured in order to work properly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After you configure pusher you will be able to enable the desktop notifications as shown in the image below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"142\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/desktop-notifications-1024x142.png\" alt=\"Desktop Notifications with Pusher.com\" class=\"wp-image-2020\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/desktop-notifications-1024x142.png 1024w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/desktop-notifications-300x42.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/desktop-notifications-768x106.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/desktop-notifications-60x8.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/desktop-notifications-150x21.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/07\/desktop-notifications.png 1228w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert- \">Starting from September 2017 the application must run on SSL in order desktop notifications to work properly (browsers requires SSL).<\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert- \">Desktop notifications does not work in Incognito mode in Chrome browser<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This option is for real-time notifications, which means that you won&#8217;t need to refresh the page in case there is a notification. Before, when new notifications for a user was added you needed to refresh the page in order the notifications to be updated. Now in this case the notification will be real time and [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[31],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1683","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-setup-and-configuration"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1683","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/typ